O.C.G.A. Section 12-9, et seq.<br>
Authority Ga. L. 1967, p. 581 et seq., as amended; Ga. L. 1972,
pp. 1015, 1058, as amended; Ga. L. 1978, p. 275, et seq., as
amended (Ga. Code Ann., Sec. 43-2701, et seq.); The Georgia Air
Quality Act of 1978, O.C.G.A. Sec. 12-9-1 et seq. History.
Original Rule entitled &quot;Permits&quot; was filed on September
6, 1973; effective September 26, 1973. Amended: Filed June 30,
1975; effective July 20, 1975. Amended: Filed October 31, 1975;
effective November 20, 1975. Amended: Filed March 20, 1979;
effective April 9, 1979. Amended: Filed August 27, 1982; effective
September 16, 1982. Amended: Filed December 9, 1986; effective
December 29, 1986. Amended: F. Dec. 20, 1990; eff. Jan. 9, 1991.
Amended: F. Aug. 27, 1992; eff. Sept. 16, 1992. Amended: F. Nov.
2, 1992; eff. Nov. 22, 1992. Amended: F. Jul. 1, 1993; eff. Jul.
21, 1993. Amended: F. Oct. 28, 1993; eff. Nov. 17,1993. Amended:
