<h3>PROPOSED GUIDANCE</h3>

<p>Draft Guidance for Selecting Media Remediation Levels at RCRA
Solid Waste Management Units; public comment period has been
extended through August 30, 1996. Outlines requirements for
performing human and ecological risk assessments at RCRA
facilities, selection of risk-based remediation levels, and
guidelines for alternate delineation strategies. Document is
available for review and copying (no charge) at the EPD Hazardous
Waste Branch, 205 Butler St., Suite 1154, Atlanta, GA 30334. EPD
Contact: Mr. Bill Mundy (404) 656-7802. </p>
