<DOCHDR>
http://www.dnr.state.ga.us:80/EPD/Apb/asb-act.htm 167.193.53.2 19970121111631 text/html 23450
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 11:20:00 GMT
