   <TITLE>Watts Bar Nuclear Plant</TITLE>
   <META NAME="Author" CONTENT="Jim Hardeman">
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.0b5aGold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000EE" VLINK="#551A8B" ALINK="#FF0000" BACKGROUND="whttxtr1.jpg">

<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Watts Bar Nuclear Plant&nbsp;</H2>

<P>Unit 1 of the Tennessee Valley Authority (TVA) Watts Bar Nuclear Plant
began commercial operation during 1996. EPD uses the <A HREF="sequoyah.html">Sequoyah
Nuclear Plant</A> network to monitor for any potential radiological effects
due to the operation of Watts Bar.</P>

