and the owner or operator of any source subject to any requirement
under 40 Code of Federal Regulations (hereinafter, CFR), Part
52.21 as amended.
<LI>Definitions: For the purpose of this section, 40 CFR, Part
52.21 (b) as amended, is hereby incorporated by reference.
</ol>
