<LI><a name=08></a>New Source Performance Standards.
<ol type=a>
<LI>General Requirement. No person shall construct or operate
any facility or source which fails to comply with the New Source
Performance Standards contained in 40 Code of Federal Regulations
(hereinafter, CFR), Part 60, as amended, including but not limited
to (unless specifically excluded below), the subparts hereby adopted
through incorporation by reference in paragraph (b) of this subsection.
<LI>New Source Performance Standards.
<ol type=1>
