<title>391-3-11 Small Business Assistance Administration.</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#0000FF" vlink="#808099" alink="#FF0000">
<h4>391-3-11 Small Business Assistance Administration.</h4>
<p>
Pursuant to the Georgia Air Quality Act, O.C.G.A. Section 12-9-25, the
Manager, on behalf of the Board of Natural Resources, shall implement
the small business stationary source technical and environmental
compliance program.
<hr>
<P>
<font size=2>
Authority: The Georgia Air Quality Act, O.C.G.A. Sec. 12-9-1,
et seq. History. Original Rule entitled &quot;Small Business Assistance
Administration&quot; adopted. F. Nov. 2, 1992; eff Nov. 22, 1992.
</font>
</DOC>
