<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p><center><strong>RULES</center>
</strong>

<p><strong><center>OF</center>
</strong>

<p><strong><center>GEORGIA DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL RESOURCES</center>
</strong>

<p><strong><center>ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION DIVISION</center>
</strong>

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p><strong><center>CHAPTER 391-3-6</center>
</strong>

<p><strong><center>WATER QUALITY CONTROL</center>
</strong>

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p><center>TABLE OF CONTENTS</center>


<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p><strong>391-3-6-.01	Organization and Administration</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.02	Preparation and Submission of Engineering
Reports, Plans and Specifications, and
Environmental Information Documents</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.03	Water Use Classifications and Water Quality
Standards</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.04	Marine Sanitation Devices</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.05	Emergency Actions</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.06	Waste Treatment and Permit Requirements</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.07	Surface Water Withdrawals</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.08	Pretreatment and Permit Requirements</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.09	Publicly Owned Treatment Works
Pretreatment Programs</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.10	Determinations of Categorization of
Industrial Users and Request for 
Fundamentally Different Factors Variances </strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.11	Land Disposal and Permit Requirements</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.12	Public Wastewater Treatment Plant
Classifications</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.13	Underground Injection Control</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.14	State Revolving Loan Fund</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.15	Non-Storm Water General Permit
Requirements</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.16	Storm Water Permit Requirements</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.17	Sewage Sludge (Biosolids) Requirements</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.18	 (Reserved)</strong>

<p><strong>391-3-6-.19	General Permit Land Application System
Requirements</strong>
