<p>73.	Butylbenzyl Phthalate

<p>74.	2-Chloronaphthalene

<p>75.	4-Chlorophenyl Phenyl Ether

<p>76.	Chrysene

<p>77.	Dibenzo(a,h)Anthracene

<p>78.	1,2-Dichlorobenzene

<p>79.	1,3-Dichlorobenzene

<p>80.	1,4-Dichlorobenzene

<p>81.	3,3'-Dichlorobenzidine

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p>82.	Diethyl Phthalate

<p>83.	Dimethyl Phthalate

<p>84.	Di-n-Butyl Phthalate

<p>85.	2,4-Dinitrotoluene

<p>86.	2,6-Dinitrotoluene

<p>87.	Di-n-Octyl Phthalate

<p>88.	1,2-Diphenylhydrazine

<p>89.	Fluoranthene

<p>90.	Fluorene

<p>91.	Hexachlorobenzene

<p>92.	Hexachlorobutadiene

<p>93.	Hexachlorocyclopentadiene

<p>94.	Hexachloroethane

<p>95.	Indeno(1,2,3-cd)Pyrene

<p>96.	Isophorone

<p>97.	Naphthalene

