<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p>	Pollutant		Cumulative Pollutant Loading Rate (lbs/acre)

<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p>	Arsenic				 	   37

<p>	Cadmium				   35

<p>	Copper					1338

<p>	Lead					  268

<p>	Mercury				 	    15

<p>	Nickel					  375

